Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.10,0:00:23.47,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}无止境的旅途中  止步不前之时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.47,0:00:29.74,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}我们深深地叹气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:37.43,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}再次放开了紧握的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:44.86,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}但是现在已经没有什么可怕的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:52.79,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}连接心灵之间那坚固的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.79,0:00:58.25,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}决不会被斩断
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.30,0:01:07.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}继续寻求 终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:13.77,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}在这个地方画上句号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:23.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}悲伤与愤怒 化为力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:28.02,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}命运就在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.26,0:22:45.23,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本是没有交点的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.23,0:22:45.98,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今天也
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.98,0:22:50.84,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}企图夺走我们的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.47,0:22:56.42,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即使获得了想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.42,0:22:57.42,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么却
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.42,0:23:02.40,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}无法坦率地会心一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.08,0:23:08.16,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}流出的眼泪    不代表弱小或后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.78,0:23:12.92,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}只是孕育痛苦的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:17.96,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不论什么样的瞬间与命运
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.96,0:23:26.71,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}终于明白了唯一可以确定的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.71,0:23:29.26,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}极限也好  困难也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:33.28,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都不愿意放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.28,0:23:38.14,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就这样决不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:45.97,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}紧握你的右手传来的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.97,0:23:49.64,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,750)\blur2}就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.68,0:01:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就像是迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意不要掉队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.61,0:01:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.98,0:01:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.39,0:01:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.89,0:01:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.32,0:01:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是炸药
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.61,0:02:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这完全潮掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会爆炸的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 别磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追兵马上就会追来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴风雪过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始准备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.32,0:02:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 长官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利及其中央派来的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合计三人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看准空隙做掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.98,0:02:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 长官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由这里的成员执行作战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:02:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对北方司令部的人也要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:03:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…迈尔斯少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做掉是指杀死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不赞成杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封印他的炼金术 叫他说出情报比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得那家伙会说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.22,0:03:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他活着太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 那家伙的部下呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人也许只是被迫变成合成兽而听命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但毕竟只是“也许”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只因为可疑就杀死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷文中将那件事 也许还有别的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了布里克斯的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放松警惕就会被干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的天真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许哪天会夺去你与同伴的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这地方不需要不谨慎的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利及另两名 就由我做掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:04:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说也是孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 在这个世界要贯穿不杀的理念太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我曾经也有那种想法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了这个年纪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经历了几场战斗后就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起杀掉 不杀才更难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔利克兄弟选择了困难的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.38,0:04:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好事的家伙们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 但是也有点羡慕他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个LaSaYaNa是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够获得长寿的灵药
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.94,0:04:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是指贤者之石呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将所有的金属转变为金
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将老人变成青年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个AUReRiAN是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金子的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽是有关长生不老与黄金的话题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡先生的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是受了清国炼丹术的影响呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在清国称不死之人为 真正的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既“真人”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是完全之人的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从金也是完全的金属这层意思上讲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有把真人称为金人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全的人是金人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一种说法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把炼金术传到清国的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是拥有金发和金瞳的长生不老之人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才这么叫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.01,0:05:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金发和金瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是爱德和阿尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 来这边 是出口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:05:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全穿越山脉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好天气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在向布里克斯进发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.53,0:06:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 你们跟着我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来雪很深呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘 坐我背上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走在前面把雪踩实开出一条路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们跟在后面就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.97,0:06:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔 不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踩到深处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.23,0:06:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么被埋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么阿尔会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿过山脉 先绕过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿过山脉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:06:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那暴风雪之中？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.22,0:07:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.76,0:07:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有迂回 笔直过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么做出这么乱来的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有紧急联络
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急联络？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央军进入了布里克斯要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姆斯壮少将也被召去中央了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在去要塞很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有藏到别的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说别的地方 我们能去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.18,0:07:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离这里不远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个叫阿斯别克的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说同胞们住在那村子的贫民窟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊修瓦尔的贫民窟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎没有别的选择呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:07:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是主人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔突然不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会被金普利怀疑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧 不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥会随机应变的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三班 三名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四班 五名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么各自开始搜索所担当的地区
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 长官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 喂 阿尔冯斯君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才应该说“好的”才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太好走动 爱德华君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 金普利在看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 金普利他们去搜查哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在城镇中央有个很大的竖坑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要进那里来调查矿道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不信任北方的部队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.46,0:09:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以只和中央都市派来的部下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙 察觉到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绕到前面去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在竖坑的附近找好狙击地点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找矿道的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有多个脚印就没错了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这个距离的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德华君…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:09:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要调查矿道的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给布里克斯兵不是更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面似乎非常复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你特意过来阻止我 也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜对了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.07,0:10:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想快点把斯卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说在争取配置狙击手的时间？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你注意到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.22,0:10:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周围有这么多杀气 当然会察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是白白活过了伊修瓦尔战争
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎在谈论什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能只瞄准金普利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开枪 要慎重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.59,0:10:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 长官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.39,0:11:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙 用雪做掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.13,0:11:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个大叔也是合成兽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 什么都看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 对方也看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.90,0:12:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半斤对八两…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖待着 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在视野不好的地区
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无法从我们的鼻子下逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈尔斯少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有合成兽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我习惯在视野不好的地方战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要进入雪烟里面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.45,0:13:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 这样个子会变矮的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸药？不愧是矿山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别靠近哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道这是什么吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 那种潮了的东西无法用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔们 知道炸药的原料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硝化甘油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硝化甘醇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木屑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有硝酸铵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 那个硝酸氨是什么组成的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是硝酸和氨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氨？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么味道？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.55,0:13:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是氨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼻子太灵也很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.01,0:14:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们已经没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心人质 马上就这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想让你把知道的事情全都说出来罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 血气方刚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤刚好就和年轻人战斗 看来会费点力气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我也没空陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我用这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己拿出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼成阵也无法用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:14:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.16,0:15:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不杀的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很伟大的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 在战场上会变成空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那一瞬 你把我杀了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.42,0:15:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那份天真就是你的败因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉进竖坑了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真过份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.59,0:16:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 金普利那家伙去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.88,0:16:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔？怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又被牵走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:00.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被什么牵走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎么了 铠甲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.03,0:17:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.55,0:17:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔 阿尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵魂被牵走…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.87,0:17:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐 以前有过这种事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能这样 让她哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 金普利那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 钢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.71,0:18:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么救了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别误会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.28,0:18:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有帮我把插在肚子上东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔掉的家伙… 会很困扰…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们把那根钢筋拔出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是敌人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有接到杀你的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 拔掉钢筋的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你立刻就会因大量失血而死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔掉的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:18:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在大出血之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用炼金术…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封住伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会用医疗系的炼金术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要人体炼成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概研究过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样子估计内脏完全乱七八糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若不像金普利那样使用贤者之石的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为贤者之石的替代品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然寿命也许会减少
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.47,0:19:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是犹豫的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是自己的天真导致的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.41,0:19:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要自己补上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你没有犹豫的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要拔了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:19:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把自己的生命想像成一种能量体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.61,0:20:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和贤者之石一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我现在是份量为灵魂的贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.17,0:20:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个使用生命的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.06,0:21:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别擅自把我杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.21,0:21:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有完全治好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把没事的组织连接起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.14,0:21:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时止血的急救措施
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 必须得去看医生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没有那个闲工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.08,0:21:23.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去追金普利才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.15,0:21:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家很…危…险
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.55,0:21:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 他是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种状态去战斗也没胜算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.44,0:21:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是金普利先生拿着的那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.44,0:21:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要叫他 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.61,0:21:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我们也卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.88,0:21:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 和那家伙说再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.12,0:22:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们算在这里死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.70,0:22:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.35,0:22:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 这家伙怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.54,0:22:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总不能让他死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.88,0:22:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我们的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.33,0:22:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.52,0:22:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了外面要先去找医生才行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.01,0:23:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斩断胶着的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.67,0:24:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开创道路所需要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.06,0:24:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意外的想法和行动力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.11,0:24:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现了隐藏之真实的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.53,0:24:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够抓住通向胜利的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.79,0:24:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那需要每天的积累
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.04,0:24:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.56,0:24:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.17,0:24:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第42话 反击的征兆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.46,0:24:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 战争即将开始
